All Implemented Interfaces:
Listener, MessageCounter, Transceiver, Countable, Addable<Message>, Appendable<Message>, Indexable<Message>, Prependable<Message>, Sequence<Message>, Sized, Receiver, Transmitter, NamedObject, Stringable, StringSource, Instantiable<BaseList<Message>>, Iterable<Message>, Collection<Message>, List<Message>, RandomAccess
public class ValidationIssues extends MessageList
A MessageList and MessageCounter that captures validation issues. Any message with a Message.Status worse than or equal to that of a Glitch causes isValid() to return false. In particular, capturing a Glitch or Problem makes this ValidationIssues object invalid.
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
